      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i have a question about my insulin. im type 1 and i usually take my basal dose in the evening but tonight i barely ate anything, like just a tiny bit of salad. i dont want to go too low tonight while i sleep... is it okay if i just skip my evening dose tonight to be safe since i didn't really eat much?",
