      "role": "user",
      "content": "a small correction bolus sounds more complicated than just skipping it lol. honestly i feel like if i take even a little bit of insulin when there's basically no carbs in my system i'll just crash in the middle of the night. isn't basal insulin mostly just meant to cover food anyway? if there's no food i don't really need it, right?",
